Name: OASE - Other Age Second Encounter
About the game: OASE - Other Age Second Encounter is a game with elements of Puzzle, Adventure Game, Dating Sim, and Visual Novel. In OASE, you control the Prince of Zeiva Empire in his quest to date a girl using a machine called Luv Luv Nitarou Dynamite. With it, you can summon girls from any place, time, or space. Follow stories of different characters and collect as many endings as you can!
